# ngx_http_waf_module - AI / LLM crawler User-Agent signatures
#
# $waf_type = ai-crawler. Flag-only: surfaced for the operator, never blocked
# by waf_bot_block. Checked BEFORE crawler.list, so AI-specific variants
# (e.g. Applebot-Extended, Google-Extended) win over their generic crawler
# counterparts. One case-insensitive PCRE2 fragment per line.
#
# Sources: ai.robots.txt, Matomo bots.yml. Drifts fast -- reload to update.

